    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it spotless and staying on top of every single service. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that 'new car' magic. You\u2019ve really got to see it in person to believe how pristine it is! I'm super friendly and happy to chat, so feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
